cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS

The paper proposes a new approach for solving high-dimensional multi-objective decision problems using deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
